        <div>
            <h1>About</h1>
            <p> 
                My name's Victor Schweitz, a 24 year old MMD student at KEA with a big passion for web development and developing my skills in that field.
            </p>
        </div>
        <img src="src/images/profile_image.jpg" class="profile-image" alt="profile_image">

        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
    </Section>


    <Section id="skills">
        <div>
